Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.94,0:00:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.27,0:00:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你把大家給……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.38,0:00:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有殺掉他們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人殺人的時代早已過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是讓他們不能再動了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.41,0:01:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人是守墓人的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.83,0:01:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽是在我七歲時去世的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.29,0:01:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村裏的人對變成孤兒的我說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.61,0:01:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起小艾就是守墓人了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾法大人曾是那麼優秀的守墓人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.68,0:01:55.63,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於我們 守墓人是不可缺少的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有小艾才能勝任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.11,0:02:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有繼承阿爾法大人血統的小艾才能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.74,0:02:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 小艾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.87,0:02:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是守墓人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.00,0:02:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那天開始我成為了村子的守墓人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從媽媽死後 村裏再也沒死過人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還是堅持每天建墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是守墓人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:24.03,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(172,624)\blur3\fad(800,0)}死之穀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期一 神創造了世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期二 神劃分了條理與混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期三 神調整了細微的數值
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期四 神允許了時光流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼各位 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:05:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期五 神看盡了世界每個角落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期六 神休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 神在星期天……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 丟棄了這個世界 -
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個世界可能已經滿員了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.42,0:05:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的世界也即將走到盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神說完這句話拋棄世界那天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人就不再死亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.51,0:05:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是心臟停止跳動 身體腐爛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死人仍沒有停止行動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說為了救贖那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:06:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為最後的奇跡 神派來了守墓人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 小艾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓阿爾法大人安心的長眠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你才能做到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有讓守墓人來埋葬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才可以使死去人們停止行動安然長眠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看我都是個威嚴的優秀守墓人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小艾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猶特叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威嚴 要有威嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大夥 小艾回來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 做為守墓人我向大家問好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝今天也會是美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:10.57,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有曲奇哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我烤了蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…大家…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你們幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過不要給守墓人大人零食嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 艾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#￥%%%@#
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 回家吧 安娜在等你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大家 過好每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見 小艾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.63,0:08:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安娜媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾 你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安娜好臭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾 這是香水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.73,0:08:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不搽那個也行 我喜歡安娜的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人的嗜好等你長大了就會懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人就會這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽去世後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耀基和安娜就收養了我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這世上的某個地方我還有親生爸爸在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字叫漢普尼韓伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽說他總有一天會來見我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時常會覺得很難過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子才十二歲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明還只是孩子 卻讓她背負如此重任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能收養這個孩子 我很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時代能有個孩子 好像做夢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子是否覺得幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耀基和安娜時偶會用傷心的眼神看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有不能對我說的秘密一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總共四十七個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挖了跟村裏人數量一樣多的墳墓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那從明天開始我要做點什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾去幫大家做點活兒好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是這裏的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會說話嗎 還是傻子？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能說話的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫艾 是守墓人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.03,0:11:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你？這裏的守墓人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 隨便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.55,0:11:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能問你這個守墓人點事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題  搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道哈娜 或者自稱是哈娜的人嗎 不論生死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 沒聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加一個下一問
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想找出有以下特徵的一個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年齡三十至四十歲 茶色頭髮 黑眼睛 五官分明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我差不身高 胸很小 這個也是不論生死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安娜年紀相仿 但是胸很大 而耀基是男的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 不是這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 那個 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有話說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…你…對了 你是誰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？對哈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食人玩具 漢普尼韓伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.64,0:13:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 跟我爸爸一樣的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是漢普尼韓伯特先生呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 這你也信！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人會叫這種名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.87,0:13:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸就叫這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.45,0:13:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你有父母啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣？你老爸叫漢普尼韓伯特先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:14:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 媽媽告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說總有一天爸爸會來見我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你是我爸爸對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能像是你老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是有點奇怪哈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想像中的爸爸應該是四十歲左右男子漢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.14,0:14:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登場應該是正英勇的與怪物對決中才對嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的絕對不是這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 那都是小問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太誇張了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸就是爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.21,0:14:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想正常與我談話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:14:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事啦 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 是守墓人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼能拜託你一項工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拜託守墓人的工作還能有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耀基？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是小艾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猶特爺爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小艾 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…你頭上的傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊 也不疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之出大事了 趕快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小艾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼那種眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我 小艾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別像看怪物一樣看我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下別動 小艾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那小子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吆！那邊那個會說話的僵屍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正準備發射三十發豆大的鉛彈覆蓋那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩秒後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 漏網了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的傢伙全部對準腦袋幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你把大家給…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺掉了是嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有殺掉他們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是我爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸是不會做這種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不是我爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.98,0:18:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就告訴你不是了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埋了他們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你準備跟我到什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你以後準備怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是守墓人...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是守墓人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初 我以為有那個不行的神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.82,0:20:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會有像你這樣半調子的守墓人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.66,0:20:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先就是這點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守墓人沒有父母
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.42,0:20:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙像蒼蠅一樣滋生出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能會有父母
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.33,0:20:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…村裏人都叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.93,0:20:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你守墓人是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.93,0:21:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又有什麼可以證明你是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得他們一直在騙你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.73,0:21:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我媽媽是叫阿爾法的守墓人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸叫漢普尼韓伯特…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說漢普尼韓伯特只是個童話人物嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發條壞了 永遠停不下來的玩具的名字而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也只是借用了這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.02,0:21:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽也是一樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不懂村裏人到底想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓像你這樣的孩子相信自己是守墓人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻又說你有父母
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底...是什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相在黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.11,0:21:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 確切說是在墳墓之下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你 把大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.15,0:22:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想殺我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.02,0:22:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是守墓人的話 一開始就不會有恨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是守墓人 就不會打神聖的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.63,0:22:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是守墓人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.83,0:22:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.30,0:22:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 即使如此 也是守墓人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.07,0:22:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.26,0:22:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的守墓人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.62,0:22:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的才是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.03,0:23:52.11,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(642,464)\fad(500,0)}死之穀 2
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“這位”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.36,0:23:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我是殺手”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.50,0:23:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“就是所謂沒有了神的夜晚”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.74,0:23:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“跟...跟我無關哦”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.52,0:23:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我是...我是守墓人！我是不會忘記的”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
