Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:18.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}在崎嶇的道路上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:21.70,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}對深信的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:24.42,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}也開始起疑惑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:30.00,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}何謂真正的幸福
